{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-index-js","path":"/","result":{"data":{"hero":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Innovative Visionary: Meet","name":"Sadiq Ahmed","subtitle":"Transforming Ideas into Digital Reality","buttonText":"Let's Connect"},"html":"<p>Web Architect | Laravel | PHP | Crafting seamless &#x26; high-performance web experiences—portfolios, e-commerce, and beyond.\nLet’s build something extraordinary!</p>"}}]},"about":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"About Me","avatar":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/06b59c2bbbc82d6d550c53eda8451fbf/b3cab/me.jpg","srcSet":"/static/06b59c2bbbc82d6d550c53eda8451fbf/477ba/me.jpg 175w,\n/static/06b59c2bbbc82d6d550c53eda8451fbf/b3cab/me.jpg 300w","srcWebp":"/static/06b59c2bbbc82d6d550c53eda8451fbf/5ba9d/me.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/06b59c2bbbc82d6d550c53eda8451fbf/9fca7/me.webp 175w,\n/static/06b59c2bbbc82d6d550c53eda8451fbf/5ba9d/me.webp 300w","sizes":"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px"}}},"skills":["Laravel","PHP","JavaScript","Mysql","CSS","HTML","Nginx","Apache","Linux","Python"]},"html":"<p>Backend Architect | Problem Solver | Web Innovator\nI’m a full-stack developer with over 3 years of experience, specializing in backend development with PHP and Laravel. I create high-performance, scalable web applications that solve real-world problems and enhance user experiences.</p>\n<p>Here’s what I can build for you:</p>\n<p>=> Portfolio Websites – Make a lasting impression with a personalized online presence that highlights your skills.</p>\n<p>=> E-commerce Platforms – Secure, seamless, and optimized stores to grow your business online.</p>\n<p>=> Business Management Systems – Custom solutions to streamline workflows, manage data, and improve efficiency.</p>\n<p>=> Custom Web Applications – Have a unique idea? I’ll turn it into a functional, scalable solution tailored to your needs.</p>\n<p>I go beyond just coding—I focus on understanding your vision and delivering solutions that are intuitive, reliable, and built for success.</p>\n<p>Connect with me today, and let’s bring your project to life!</p>\n<p>Here is a list of the technologies that I'm familiar with!</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Backend Developement","company":"Laravel","range":"-","url":"https://www.laravel.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Laravel is a free open-source PHP framework. It provides web developers tools and resources for building modern PHP web applications.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Laravel has useful built-in features like the Artisan command-line interface (CLI), native authentication and model-view-controller (MVC) architecture. These features make the framework easy to use and are the main reason for its popularity.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Laravel is a trendy web framework. It has more than 70,000 stars on GitHub and has become an in-demand skill on the job market.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Backend Developement","company":"PHP","range":"March 2019 - Present","url":"https://www.php.net/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>The PHP Hypertext Preprocessor (PHP) is a programming language that allows web developers to create dynamic content that interacts with databases. PHP is basically used for developing web based software applications. This tutorial helps you to build your base with PHP.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>PHP is a server side scripting language that is embedded in HTML. It is used to manage dynamic content, databases, session tracking, even build entire e-commerce sites. It is integrated with a number of popular databases, including MySQL, PostgreSQL, Oracle, Sybase, Informix, and Microsoft SQL Server.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Web Development","company":"JS","range":"-","url":"#"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p>JavaScript (JS) is a lightweight, interpreted, or just-in-time compiled programming language with first-class functions. While it is most well-known as the scripting language for Web pages, many non-browser environments also use it, such as Node.js, Apache CouchDB and Adobe Acrobat. JavaScript is a prototype-based, multi-paradigm, single-threaded, dynamic language, supporting object-oriented, imperative, and declarative (e.g. functional programming) styles.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>JavaScript's dynamic capabilities include runtime object construction, variable parameter lists, function variables, dynamic script creation (via eval), object introspection (via for...in and Object utilities), and source-code recovery (JavaScript functions store their source text and can be retrieved through toString()).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Web-Based File Manager","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5625,"src":"/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/60290/demo.png","srcSet":"/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/847ef/demo.png 175w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/91cba/demo.png 350w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/60290/demo.png 700w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/f5f50/demo.png 1050w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/38674/demo.png 1400w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/4fced/demo.png 1525w","srcWebp":"/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/89afa/demo.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/9fca7/demo.webp 175w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/37a4e/demo.webp 350w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/89afa/demo.webp 700w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/78e7a/demo.webp 1050w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/03d34/demo.webp 1400w,\n/static/fc30f49bf641ec122c8547bca5e7ad1a/b513b/demo.webp 1525w","sizes":"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"}}},"tech":["PHP 8","Laravel"],"github":"https://github.com/sadiq-bd/file-manager","external":"https://github.com/sadiq-bd/file-manager"},"html":"<p>Simple File Manager for manag